creator: Bigtech Platforms
descriptionHtml:
With Mi OTT you have on your cell phone, tablet, computer and any device all the content you want! movies, series, news, sports, etc... Wherever you are and whenever you want, you only need internet or WiFi.

You can also find educational content and more for the whole family.

My OTT is a streaming platform that brings audio-visual content from the world leading film studios and local producers to your hands, with genres for all tastes:

✓  Movies
✓  Series
✓  Documentaries
✓  Sports news and events
✓  World news
✓ The classic and modern soap operas that you like
✓  National, regional and local programming
✓  For children and young people
✓ Educational and fun content

Our programming is tailored to meet your preferences.

No more races to not miss your favorite shows, now you see them wherever you are, at the time you want, you just need to have internet or WiFi and your preferred device.

Try it today!

creator: Master Link de México, S.A. de C.V.
descriptionHtml:
We are an OTT service that offers new opportunities for your business by offering TV online and V.O.D. licensed without the need for equipment or wiring, with the purpose of entertaining thanks to our wide variety of content through the access of an application on multiple devices.

You can also find educational content and more for the whole family.


 Movies
 Series
 Documentaries
 Sport news and events
 World news
 The classic and modern soap operas that you like
 National, regional and local programming
 For children and young people
 Educational and fun content

The app has the following features:
o More than 70 channels
o Multi-device
o Portable
o Premium content
o Has the best channels
o And much more
